            td <div><a href="https://www.twitter.com/" target='_blank'>Join us on Twitter</a> <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dtn38ytgc/image/upload/v1614803760/templates/gorjeo_orky7q.png" class="icon"></img></div>
